r-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: sol=
id; background-color: #ccc;"> Anyway</a>:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin=
: 16px 0;">Nikola Corp. founder and former chairman Trevor Milton has been =
charged by prosecutors with making false statements to investors in the ele=
ctric-vehicle startup.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Milton, who stepped =
down from the company in September, is in federal custody after voluntarily=
 surrendering. He=E2=80=99s charged with misleading investors from November=
 2019 until about September 2020 with the development of Nikola=E2=80=99s p=
roducts and technology, according to an indictment unsealed Thursday by fed=
eral prosecutors in N.Y. The Securities and Exchange Commission also filed =
a complaint against him.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here =
are the <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24592602.2=
