erage portfolio was margined under CS=E2=80=99s Standard Margin Procedure, =
with dynamic margining to factor in changes to its portfolio characteristic=
s (volatility, concentration, bias, etc.). By contrast, Archegos=E2=80=99s =
swaps with Prime Financing were statically margined. This meant that initia=
l margins were calculated based on the notional value of the swap at incept=
ion and remained static in dollar terms over the life of the swap; thus, if=
